# --- AI / IDE assistant directories ---
# Convention: track team-shared config and the engineering-memory vault,
# ignore personal runtime caches and local overrides.

# Omnix Runtime — track committed config (agents/workflows/commands/settings),
# ignore the auto-managed session cache.
.omnix/memory/
.omnix/cache/

# Obsidian-AI engineering memory vault — fully tracked.
# (Intentionally NOT ignored. Vault is the team's long-term memory.)
# Obsidian app UI state — not meaningful to track.
.obsidian-ai-memory/.obsidian/workspace.json
.obsidian-ai-memory/.obsidian/graph.json
.obsidian-ai-memory/.obsidian/cache

# Cursor — track all committed config; ignore only personal overrides.
.cursor/AGENTS.local.md
.cursor/.local/

# Claude Code project config — track .claude/ shared parts, ignore personal.
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/CLAUDE.local.md

# Stray parser scratch dirs
**/.tmp_docx_extract*/
**/.tmp_pdf_extract*/

# Generated resume exports
**/exports/*.pdf
**/exports/*.docx
